dmin-example-ach-daily-influenzatherapeutic.html\">MedicationAdministration: status = completed; medication[x] = -&gt;Oseltamivir 60 mg PO; effective[x] = 2024-01-01 20:00:00+0000 --&gt; 2024-01-04 20:00:09+0000</a></li><li><a href=\"MedicationRequest-medicationrequest-example-ach-daily-influenzatherapeutic.html\">MedicationRequest: identifier = urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.19.5.1.798#101903002\u00a0(use:\u00a0usual,\u00a0); status = completed; intent = order; category = Inpatient; medication[x] = -&gt;Oseltamivir 60 mg; authoredOn = 2024-01-01 11:45:15+0000; courseOfTherapyType = Short course (acute) therapy</a></li><li><a href=\"Immunization-immunization-example-ach-daily-influenzatherapeutic.html\">Immunization: identifier = OID:1.3.6.1.4.1.21367.2005.3.7.1234; status = completed; vaccineCode = Fluvax; occurrence[x] = 2024-01-02; primarySource = true; lotNumber = AAJN11K; expirationDate = 2025-02-15; doseQuantity = 5 mg; note = Notes on administration of vaccine; isSubpotent = true</a></li></ul></div>"
